Тест 1:
Входные данные:
departments = {
    "IT": ["Anna", "Leo"],
    "HR": ["Maria"]
}

export_company_structure('company1.xml', departments)

with open('company1.xml', 'r', encoding='utf-8') as f:
    print(f.read())

Ожидаемый вывод:
<company>
  <department name="IT">
    <employee>Anna</employee>
    <employee>Leo</employee>
  </department>
  <department name="HR">
    <employee>Maria</employee>
  </department>
</company>

